{"tid":1611943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城 Online] 鍵戰部新職業招募中 - 易容師！","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:32:07.000Z","uid":236171,"like":129,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"b946bd750761148d9bef72be0b4dc4a6171e82d7","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"[文少長，但跪求睇晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前開過 post 但係留咗啲重點<br />\n而家重新開過，求大家幫手全力推</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香城 Online 新職業上線了！<br />\n鍵戰部隊 - 易容師</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有好多仆街藍屍會偷拍義士大頭相擺上 page，令義士無論喺法律上定人身安全上都非常不利！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irUEgfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirUEgfD.jpg&h=1fcfbeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為減低佢哋對義士造成嘅傷害，我諗到呢個方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係幫起底相做 Faceswap，<br />\n然後擺翻上藍屍起底網！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要網上充斥住假嘅起底圖，而且難分真假，起底圖就自然冇參考價值！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n做法好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 喺藍屍 page 下載起底相</span></strong><br />\n__私人影嘅先做啦，炒報紙/<br />\n__直播嘅已經通晒天，無咩意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 網上搵張相，人嘅角度同表情合適就得<br />\n</strong></span>__唔好用明星相就得<br />\n__用狗公狗乸圖效果更佳<ins></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 用 App 或者 PS key 個人樣上起底圖</span></strong><br />\n__推薦 app： Cupace<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4. 用假帳號擺上另一個藍屍起底 page</strong></span><br />\n__唔好擺返落同一個 group，俾人認到<br />\n__唔洗介意俾佢哋發現係假圖。<br />\n__就係想佢哋見到張相都唔知真假。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFoHT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFoHT1.jpg&h=19766506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（呢張例圖我 hea 做嘅，表情唔合適。）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的係令佢哋好似捉鬼咁捉假圖，啲圖就會失去公信力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n啲圖唔知真假，好難呈堂<br />\n班狗跟住圖咬女義士，點知咬親阿嫂<br />\n藍屍想認樣打義士打唔到<br />\n咁我哋就成功喇!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有，好重要！x 100<br />\n為免阻礙被捕手足相認： </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 對象限做緊嘢被影大頭嘅手足<br />\n2. 做完放藍屍 page，唔好放連登<br />\n<br />\n被捕嘅手足已經俾狗 mark 晒名<br />\n所以改黎都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋鍵戰部隊除咗國際文宣同控制輿論風向之外，仲有好多嘢做架！！<br />\n義士為我哋擋子彈，我哋幫手㩒幾個掣都好應分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以求你哋大大力推，快快手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25ce0ca9f9db015bcbc3983c911ddd1edaa681f","tid":1611943,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2739a1613daf2af567097f452cd46fbe82567aa","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住個目的唔係要佢信<br />\n係要佢唔知信唔信</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8e89383e6c986b038ddaa9971ac9d1403cd07476","tid":1611943,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"8abf899bc9f31aacdaf78f610650546d061b234f","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"你哋諗下，popo喺網上搵到10張一模一樣嘅相出嚟，淨係個樣唔同咗。<br />\n<br />\n佢要逐張圖搵返個原 source 出嚟<br />\n你知啦，我哋幫記者搵 owner 都要推幾百次 post<br />\n仲要班藍屍無腦乜都鳩 forward 一餐<br />\n搵晒十個 source 難過登天呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題嚟嘞，可能嗰十張全部係假圖<br />\n真嗰張佢仲未遇到<br />\n可能全部努力都係徒勞無功</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0de928a321841198de80d1f24b6ac742ced87d","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"義士幫我哋擋子彈<br />\n我哋幫佢㩒兩個掣都唔得？"},{"pid":"153215eb5dfdd488a7aba5962286c17ac934b18f","tid":1611943,"uid":267937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c3b0e4b1e9b7b6e774e9b17bb1ce657476ccf83","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"示範下 Cupace<br />\n1. 喺主頁揀 &quot;cut face&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXE1u7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXE1u7V.jpg&h=9a38c8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 路人甲相度 crop 個樣出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3xBOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3xBOb.jpg&h=0fd1d4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 喺主頁揀 &quot;paste face&quot;<br />\n<br />\n4. 揀返塊面<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nCymgj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nCymgj.jpg&h=117c9e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 較大細光暗對比飽和<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vh4psXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvh4psXz.jpg&h=138a4a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. 搵啲港女自拍 app 整蒙少少遮蓋瑕疵<br />\n<br />\n完成！"},{"pid":"40c04021752db77d5db6e8551eb7d9a2a5da8d21","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:07:42.000Z","msg":"易容師需要每個巴絲嘅努力，先可以將效果發揮到最大！"},{"pid":"7cc68f7c92234104f44b03c0c4d838c97256b84c","tid":1611943,"uid":220260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:08:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54d9c94deb766dbd12e8d626872b2828dc1f9f0f","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"入行冇門檻！<br />\n所有人都可以加入！<br />\n<br />\n唔需要勇氣！<br />\n唔需要知識！<br />\n唔會用你好多時間！"},{"pid":"37e88bbc851df9a04e97c4313539c94646085174","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"cac24db41cf09ff0195df47a418c56c9091a7c0e","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e88bbc851df9a04e97c4313539c94646085174","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"fe00405b99f310f6e6f5b2219092adad10a5a362","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:1