" />"},{"pid":"8604a84100126449f5ee663e7413957b0cffd135","tid":1611943,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b946bd750761148d9bef72be0b4dc4a6171e82d7","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"[文少長，但跪求睇晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前開過 post 但係留咗啲重點<br />\n而家重新開過，求大家幫手全力推</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香城 Online 新職業上線了！<br />\n鍵戰部隊 - 易容師</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有好多仆街藍屍會偷拍義士大頭相擺上 page，令義士無論喺法律上定人身安全上都非常不利！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irUEgfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirUEgfD.jpg&h=1fcfbeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為減低佢哋對義士造成嘅傷害，我諗到呢個方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係幫起底相做 Faceswap，<br />\n然後擺翻上藍屍起底網！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要網上充斥住假嘅起底圖，而且難分真假，起底圖就自然冇參考價值！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n做法好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 喺藍屍 page 下載起底相</span></strong><br />\n__私人影嘅先做啦，炒報紙/<br />\n__直播嘅已經通晒天，無咩意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 網上搵張相，人嘅角度同表情合適就得<br />\n</strong></span>__唔好用明星相就得<br />\n__用狗公狗乸圖效果更佳<ins></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 用 App 或者 PS key 個人樣上起底圖</span></strong><br />\n__推薦 app： Cupace<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4. 用假帳號擺上另一個藍屍起底 page</strong></span><br />\n__唔好擺返落同一個 group，俾人認到<br />\n__唔洗介意俾佢哋發現係假圖。<br />\n__就係想佢哋見到張相都唔知真假。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFoHT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFoHT1.jpg&h=19766506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（呢張例圖我 hea 做嘅，表情唔合適。）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的係令佢哋好似捉鬼咁捉假圖，啲圖就會失去公信力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n啲圖唔知真假，好難呈堂<br />\n班狗跟住圖咬女義士，點知咬親阿嫂<br />\n藍屍想認樣打義士打唔到<br />\n咁我哋就成功喇!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有，好重要！x 100<br />\n為免阻礙被捕手足相認： </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 對象限做緊嘢被影大頭嘅手足<br />\n2. 做完放藍屍 page，唔好放連登<br />\n<br />\n被捕嘅手足已經俾狗 mark 晒名<br />\n所以改黎都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋鍵戰部隊除咗國際文宣同控制輿論風向之外，仲有好多嘢做架！！<br />\n義士為我哋擋子彈，我哋幫手㩒幾個掣都好應分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以求你哋大大力推，快快手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"求教學 點做"},{"pid":"59b732369124e141b6b9f21c22f0e64ece756fce","tid":1611943,"uid":132641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7167abf7aac66b06af2f129b36f2e1babe3a94ca","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8604a84100126449f5ee663e7413957b0cffd135","tid":1611943,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b946bd750761148d9bef72be0b4dc4a6171e82d7","tid":1611943,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"[文少長，但跪求睇晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前開過 post 但係留咗啲重點<br />\n而家重新開過，求大家幫手全力推</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香城 Online 新職業上線了！<br />\n鍵戰部隊 - 易容師</strong></span>